{"tid":1452564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[外國勢力]港共搵得公安武警, 我地就必須尋求外國既支援","createTime":"2019-08-12T01:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T03:30:54.000Z","uid":60006,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b159e6eb80838a5554534581a1a150181ae83a","tid":1452564,"uid":60006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:42:02.000Z","msg":"已經愈來愈多証據証明 港共派出公安 武警 解放軍混入香港警隊<br />\n<br />\n事情發展同俄羅斯打烏克蘭係一樣(派所謂傭兵, 正式軍從無出動), 而俄佬前幾日亦發出聲明<br />\n<br />\n而家已經唔係人民鬥人民, 係人民鬥軍隊<br />\n而且<span style=\"color: red;\">已經發生人道災難, 雖然無人死 但已經有救護人員永久殘障, 大規模化學中毒</span><br />\n<br />\n反正係唔係都比人屈外國勢力, 點解我地唔真係搵外國勢力?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請各位盡自己努力, send求助訊息比英美澳加 聯合國議員官員, 唔好再等人template, 自己寫就算寫中文都得架, 佢地一定有翻譯</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請各位每人花10分鐘到 send求助訊息(email又好Twitter又好) 比5-10位外國官員, 文宣組已經做唔切, 大家幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbadbe47d1b978d666ecb8a5b6e418984da8f7f4","tid":1452564,"uid":298714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:42:16.000Z","msg":"[案例討論] 塞爾維亞人教你，咩叫禍不及妻兒，請各位參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1448757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1448757</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/aJ3pKRC1zqY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaJ3pKRC1zqY&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=841fa55f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aJ3pKRC1zqY</a><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/T-mmZwdIg8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FT-mmZwdIg8A&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=beaf75a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/T-mmZwdIg8A</a>"},{"pid":"960f7ae57c293ec2126593d0a8987f902daa10ea","tid":1452564,"uid":60006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:51:39.0